snippet.textDisplay:
My favourite part is 2:18 - 2:54  I don't understand a word but it just sounds so mystical! 
Everything about this girl is just out of this world. Her every expression is so animated, the way she sings it and carries herself out in this song, just oozes vibrant energy. There's this sense of playfulness in the way she sang it, makes you want to be a kid again and go out in the rain dancing under the clouds in circles with this song echoing in the periphery. Thank you Sona, thanks coke studio!
